{"tid":2189523,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"杜琪峯帶契 向佐成為加拿大奇幻影帝","createTime":"2020-09-05T03:09:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T08:17:58.000Z","uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e5196f8f9e7e1e60a11b31273a1ce21798f4f579","tid":2189523,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:09:29.000Z","msg":"套片咁撚垃圾都可以得獎，外國人真係好鐘意杜sir。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望杜sir會再拍針對歐美既電影，唔好再拍大陸戲。（杜sir話過兩集黑社會同神探係針對歐美而拍既電影）<br />\n<br />\n<em>杜琪峯執導、韋家輝編劇的電影《我的拳王男友》，在加拿大加奇幻電影節帶契向佐獲最佳男主獎，是他從影14年來首個電影獎項。向佐表示很高興跟杜琪峯及韋家輝合作，又感謝家人一直以來的支持。</em><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200904/QH2UIADCAVDULJ6SSUCFA5K3JI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200904%2FQH2UIADCAVDULJ6SSUCFA5K3JI%2F&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs4yKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=0de73646\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200904%2FQH2UIADCAVDULJ6SSUCFA5K3JI%2F&h=1bc29e91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200904/QH2UIADCAVDULJ6SSUCFA5K3JI/</a>"},{"pid":"11c7a75267fd6e9bcca656ff29eb5e34f89844ad","tid":2189523,"uid":273294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:10:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"275819e3d10d938967e3604388c30b2f1edb96e2","tid":2189523,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:11:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/polish-comedy-marygoround-wins-top-prizes-at-fantasia-film-fest\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Fheat-vision%2Fpolish-comedy-marygoround-wins-top-prizes-at-fantasia-